Cable providers

Izzi Telecom (formerly known as Cablevisión México) is the internet, fixed telephony and cable TV provider of Grupo Televisa. The new brand pretends to unify all cable providers owned by Televisa across Mexico (Cablevisión DF, Cablemas, Cablevisión Monterrey, Cablecom and Telecable) to compete against Telmex.





