About Us
Grupo Televisa, S.A.B

Is the largest media company in the Spanish-speaking world a major participant in the international entertainment business.It has interests in television production broadcasting, production of pay-television networks, international distribution of television programming, direct-to-home satellite services, cable television telecommunication services, magazine publishing distribution, radio production broadcasting, professional sports live entertainment, feature-film production distribution, the operation of an internet portal, gaming.Televisa Internacional, the international distributor of content for Grupo Televisa, is the world's leading distributor of Spanish-language programming formats.


For over 50 years, our telenovelas have become international hits today we continue our legacy by offering to more than 100 countries worldwide our HDdigital TV programming which includes series, reality shows, animation movies.We also have an innovative catalogue of original formats for telenovelas, series, gamereality shows of guaranteed success backed by the expertise talent of our experts in production marketing.Televisa Internacional offers: Finished Products: The largest library of innovative content that adapts to any platform generates 360° business strategies.Formats: Hits of guaranteed success backed by our experts in production adaptable to fit your local needs.Co-productions: Building strategic alliances to create local hits.Discover more at www.televisainternacional.tv.It has it all!





Televisa Internacional



