Grupo Televisa S.A.B

Avda. Vasco de Quiroga #2000 Edif. A, Piso 4 Colonia Santa Fe
Mexico City  1210 Mexico
Phone: +52 55 ____ ____
Fax: 
http://www.televisa.com/us





11
Managers




789
IT employees




$189.7MEST.
IT Budget




Grupo Televisa S.A.B. is a Mexican mas multimedia company and the largest in Latin America and the Spanish speaking world operating in the television, film, telecommunications, radio, and publishing sectors. The company operates four broadcast channels in Mexico and produces… MoreGrupo Televisa S.A.B. is a Mexican mas multimedia company and the largest in Latin America and the Spanish speaking world operating in the television, film, telecommunications, radio, and publishing sectors. The company operates four broadcast channels in Mexico and produces 25 other pay-TV brands and channels in Mexico and 50 countries worldwide. The company also exports it's programs to the United States where it is exclusively aired on Univision.






